1. Introduction
    website: https://mui.com/
    https://mui.com/material-ui/getting-started/installation/
    
2. Install
- Install default material ui
    yarn add @mui/material@^5.13.0 (npm i @mui/material@^5.13.0)
    yarn add @emotion/react@^11.11.0 (npm i @emotion/react@^11.11.0)
    yarn add @emotion/styled@^11.11.0 (npm i @emotion/styled@^11.11.0)

- Install Roboto font
    + cách 1: npm install @fontsource/roboto
    
    + cách 2: (recommand nên dùng) dùng link đến google web fonts, dán vào file index.html
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
        <link
        rel="stylesheet"
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap"
        />

- Install  Icons
    yarn add @mui/icons-material@^5.11.16 (hoặc npm i  @mui/icons-material@^5.11.16)

3. Usage
    - khai báo font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif; để chuẩn  hóa font cho dự án
    - Xem thêm cách dùng các element trong mui.com/get-started 
